   The Last of the Free.

   At the dawn of the first millennia, there was no Scotland or England. 
   In the first episode of this landmark series, Neil Oliver reveals the 
   mystery of how the Gaelic Scottish Kingdom - Alba - was born, and why 
   its role in one of the greatest battles ever fought on British soil 
   defined the shape of Britain into the modern era.
